1
00:00:29,697 --> 00:00:32,667
-I ALWAYS IMAGINED
THERE'D BE A TIME IN MY LIFE

2
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:34,270
WHEN EVERYTHING WOULD LINE UP

3
00:00:34,302 --> 00:00:38,472
AND THE UNIVERSE WOULD
REVEAL ITS PLAN TO ME.

4
00:00:38,506 --> 00:00:40,466
WHAT WAS ONCE CONFUSING
AND OVERWHELMING

5
00:00:40,508 --> 00:00:43,778
WOULD REASSEMBLE INTO SOMETHING
SO CLEAR AND SO BRIGHT,

6
00:00:43,811 --> 00:00:47,151
THERE WAS NO WAY I WOULDN'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

7
00:00:55,156 --> 00:00:58,356
AND I GUESS YOU COULD SAY
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.

8
00:01:19,380 --> 00:01:20,850
BUT JUST LIKE THE STARS,

9
00:01:20,881 --> 00:01:23,721
THE BRIGHTEST ONES
ARE THE MOST FLEETING

10
00:01:23,751 --> 00:01:29,891
AND COLLAPSE INTO THE BIGGEST,
DEEPEST BLACK HOLES.

11
00:01:29,923 --> 00:01:32,693
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

12
00:01:40,368 --> 00:01:42,568
-* YOU JUST LET HIM

13
